The knowledge files in this repository cite established UX and accessibility
frameworks (Nielsen Norman Group's heuristics, Yablonski's Laws of UX,
Brignull's Deceptive Design taxonomy, W3C WCAG 2.2, etc.). Those sources
remain under their respective licenses or copyrights. This repository does
not redistribute the original texts; it provides educational summaries,
working notes, and audit templates inspired by them, with attribution.

If you reproduce significant portions of any cited work, refer to that
work's original license.
